---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Financial Planning" description="Nathan Bost — Financial Advisor at Edward Jones, serving clients in Durham, NC with retirement, investment, and legacy planning.">
  <div class="bg-brand-navy min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">

      <!-- Hero -->
      <header class="mb-16">
        <p class="text-brand-gold text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Financial Planning</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-cream mb-6 leading-tight">
          Financial Freedom<br class="hidden sm:block" /> Starts With a Plan.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-brand-cream/70 text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          I've been a Financial Advisor at Edward Jones since December 2020, serving clients in
          the Durham, NC area. I believe financial planning is ultimately about freedom — the
          freedom to live generously, wisely, and with purpose.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Services grid -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-gold mb-8">How I Can Help</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

          <div class="bg-brand-slate/50 border border-brand-slate rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-brand-gold text-2xl mb-3">📈</div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-cream font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Retirement Planning</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-cream/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Build a clear path toward retirement — whether that's 5 years away or 30.
              Investment strategy, tax efficiency, and income planning that actually fits your life.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-brand-slate/50 border border-brand-slate rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-brand-gold text-2xl mb-3">🎓</div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-cream font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Education & Life Goals</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-cream/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              From college funding to major life milestones — practical strategies to save
              intentionally and reach the goals that matter most to your family.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-brand-slate/50 border border-brand-slate rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-brand-gold text-2xl mb-3">🏛</div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-cream font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Estate & Legacy Planning</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-cream/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Think through what you want to leave behind — for your family, your faith
              community, and the causes you care about. Coordinate with your estate documents.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-brand-slate/50 border border-brand-slate rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-brand-gold text-2xl mb-3">🧭</div>
            <h3 class="text-brand-cream font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Ongoing Guidance</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-cream/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Markets change. Life changes. I'm here for the long haul — regular check-ins,
              portfolio reviews, and a trusted voice when decisions get complicated.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- About Edward Jones callout -->
      <section class="bg-brand-slate/30 border border-brand-gold/20 rounded-xl p-8 mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-gold mb-3">Edward Jones — Durham, NC</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-cream/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Edward Jones is one of the most trusted names in financial services, built on a
          simple model: a dedicated advisor who knows you personally, in your community.
          I work with individuals, families, and business owners — focusing on relationships
          over transactions and long-term outcomes over short-term noise.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-cream/50 text-sm mb-4">
          Serving clients in Durham, Chapel Hill, and the greater Triangle area since 2020.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://www.edwardjones.com/us-en/financial-advisor/nathan-bost"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-gold text-sm font-medium hover:text-brand-gold-light transition-colors"
        >
          View my Edward Jones profile &rarr;
        </a>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-brand-cream/60 mb-6 text-lg">Ready to start the conversation?</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://www.edwardjones.com/us-en/financial-advisor/nathan-bost"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-block bg-brand-gold text-brand-navy font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-gold-light transition-colors text-lg"
          >
            Visit My Edward Jones Profile
          </a>
          <a
            href="mailto:nbost130@gmail.com"
            class="inline-block border border-brand-gold text-brand-gold font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand-gold/10 transition-colors text-lg"
          >
            Email Me Directly
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
